</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umcdermit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mcdermit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/9/01 9:13:25 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src="http://members.home.com/zwobu/z.jpeg" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to Gems drop?</span><hr size=1> For arms and legs, the gems drop off of Wyverns and Cobalt Drakes in Cobalt Scar. Very good hunting for a solo Wizard at 44 or so, and you can get 3 of each very quickly, especially if you trade other class' gems that you find for your own.<br>
<br>
For bracer, helm, gloves and boots go hunt spiders in Velk's Lab. Great place for XP from 50-60. These also drop in Wakening lands off of Suits of Sentient Armor, but those will definately require a group effort.<br>
<br>
Robe gems can be found in Dragon Necropolis I hear.<br>
 <p>Zwobu&nbsp;&lt;Trade&nbsp;Foundation&gt;&nbsp;Innoruuk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyulle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yulle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/12/01 6:56:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where to Gems drop?</span><hr size=1> Arms, Leggings - Wyverns of Cobalt Scars(They also drop Arms/Leggings gems for melee/priest)<br>
<br>
Bracer, Helm, Gloves, and Boots - Velketor's Labyrinth(50+), Sirens Grotto(recommended, if you're 55+.), Wakening Lands(Suit of Sentinel Armor, You can hunt them with 52ish small group.) , Cobalt Scars(Bulthars), Dragon Necropolis(55+)<br>
<br>
Robe (or BP for another classes) - Velketor's Labyrinth(Deep Side of Kobold Pits - High Level Spiders/Terror or so), Sirens Grotto(near Sirens Castle), Dragon Necropolis<br>
<br>
